A bright future begins with healthy meals and beautiful schools






Hundreds of school districts partner with us to manage their nutrition and facilities services.







You want the best for your students and so do we. With great care and expertise we provide student-approved nutritious meals and cutting-edge facilities service. We take great pride in creating the ideal environment where your students can grow and succeed. Working together we can deliver the best solutions for your district.





Aramark serves nearly 370 million meals on a yearly basis to more than 2 million children.










