Aramark Schools Facilities, LLC Overview
  Aramark Schools Facilities, LLC filed as a Foreign Limited Liability in the State of Florida on Tuesday, November 25, 2008 and is approximately nine years old, according to public records filed with Florida Department of State. A corporate filing is called a foreign filing when an existing corporate entity files in a state other than the state they originally filed in. This does not necessarily mean that they are from outside the United States.   




