Company Overview of ARAMARK Schools Facilities, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ARAMARK Schools Facilities, LLC was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. ARAMARK Schools Facilities, LLC operates as a subsidiary of ARAMARK Corporation.


1101 Market StreetPhiladelphia, PA 19107United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 215-238-3000








